Program: Omnibus
Title: Simone de Beauvoir
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jtw
Last Broadcast Date: 24 April 1990
Biographer Deirdre Bair talks about the feminist writer and author of 'The Second Sex', looking at her personal life, at how De Beauvoir's feminist theories developed and how the world reacted to her book.